
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Capsule' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Capsule rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Plica syndrome' radio button is enabled
And 'Arthritis' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Plica syndrome' radio button
Then 'Prominent Plica humeroradialis' checkbox is enabled

And 'Posterolateral ' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Anterior' checkbox is enabled

And 'Joint effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Local chondropathy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Local synovial Inflammation' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Prominent Plica humeroradialis' checkbox
Then 'Thickening' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ill-defined' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Thickening' checkbox
Then '> 3 mm maximum extension' checkbox is enabled
